### ============================================================
### Linguist LLM Gateway — Admin API Reference
### ============================================================
###
### 使用：安装 VSCode 扩展 "REST Client"，修改下方变量后点击 "Send Request"
### 这个文件严格遵循全局 DRY 规范（一个端点字面量仅声明一次）。
###
### 架构三层模型：
###   Provider → ProviderModel → VirtualModel
###
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:3622
@adminEmail = admin@example.com
@adminPassword = changeme123

# === 全局端点定义 (DRY规范: 一个端点只写一次) ===
@api = {{baseUrl}}/api
@loginEp          = {{api}}/login
@meEp             = {{api}}/me
@usersEp          = {{api}}/users
@providersEp      = {{api}}/providers
@providerModelsEp = {{api}}/provider-models
@virtualModelsEp  = {{api}}/virtual-models
@requestLogsEp    = {{api}}/request-logs
@appsEp           = {{api}}/apps
@oauthCopilotEp   = {{api}}/oauth/copilot
@statsEp          = {{api}}/stats

# === 请求变量链 (自动注入后续请求) ===
# 运行相关 POST 请求后，生成的 ID 将自动注入下方变量
@adminToken      = {{login.response.body.access_token}}
@providerId      = {{create_provider.response.body.id}}
@providerModelId = {{create_provider_model.response.body.id}}
@virtualModelId  = {{create_virtual_model.response.body.id}}
@appId           = {{create_app.response.body.id}}
@apiKeyId        = {{create_api_key.response.body.id}}
@userId          = {{create_user.response.body.id}}

# === 测试用的预设 ID ===
@fixedProviderId      = a3b4c5d6
@fixedProviderModelId = 00000001
@fixedVirtualModelId  = vm000001
@fixedAppId           = app_a1b2c3d4
@fixedApiKeyId        = key00001
@fixedRequestLogId    = c9f5c1c7-1da2-4e8d-9c1a-ffd20c967bda
@deviceCode           = TEST_DEVICE_CODE
@fixedUserId          = abcdef12

### ============================================================
### 0. Auth & Users（认证与用户）
### ============================================================

### 0.1 获取管理员 Token (登录)
# @name login
POST {{loginEp}} HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
    "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

###

### 0.2 获取当前登录用户
GET {{meEp}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 0.3 列出所有用户
# 参数示例: ?limit=10&starting_after=abc...&search=admin
GET {{usersEp}}?limit=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 0.4 创建新用户
# @name create_user
POST {{usersEp}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "newuser",
    "email": "user@example.com",
    "password": "strongpassword",
    "avatar_data": ""
}

###

### 0.5 更新用户 (支持所有字段可选修改)
POST {{usersEp}}/{{fixedUserId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "updated_name",
    "is_active": false
}

###

### 0.6 获取用户头像 (公开接口，无需 Token)
GET {{usersEp}}/{{fixedUserId}}/avatar HTTP/1.1

###

### 0.7 删除用户
DELETE {{usersEp}}/{{fixedUserId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###


### ============================================================
### 1. Provider（提供商）
### ============================================================

### 1.1 创建提供商
# @name create_provider
POST {{providersEp}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "深度求索",
    "kind": "deepseek",
    "base_url": "https://api.deepseek.com/v1",
    "api_key": "sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx"
}

###

### 1.2 列出所有提供商
GET {{providersEp}}?limit=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 1.3 查询单个提供商
GET {{providersEp}}/{{fixedProviderId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 1.4 更新提供商
POST {{providersEp}}/{{fixedProviderId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "DeepSeek (Updated)",
    "is_active": true
}

###

### 1.5 删除提供商
DELETE {{providersEp}}/{{fixedProviderId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###


### ============================================================
### 2. ProviderModel（提供商模型）
### ============================================================

### 2.1 创建提供商模型
# @name create_provider_model
POST {{providerModelsEp}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "provider_id": "{{fixedProviderId}}",
    "name": "deepseek-v4-pro",
    "model_type": "chat",
    "capabilities": ["tools", "thinking"],
    "supported_parameters": ["temperature", "top_p", "stop", "reasoning_effort"],
    "parameters": {
        "max_tokens": 16000,
        "context_window": 128000
    },
    "pricing_tiers": [
        { "startTokens": 0, "maxTokens": 32000, "inputPrice": 0.001, "outputPrice": 0.002, "cachePrice": 0.0001 }
    ]
}

###

### 2.1.1 Create chat model with supported_parameters
POST {{providerModelsEp}} HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "provider_id": "{{fixedProviderId}}",
  "name": "deepseek-v4-flash",
  "model_type": "chat",
  "capabilities": ["stream", "tools", "vision"],
  "supported_parameters": ["temperature", "top_p", "frequency_penalty", "presence_penalty", "stop"],
  "parameters": {
      "max_tokens": 8192
  }
}

###

### 2.1.2 Create embedding model with supported_parameters
POST {{providerModelsEp}} HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "provider_id": "{{fixedProviderId}}",
  "name": "text-embedding-3-small",
  "model_type": "embedding",
  "capabilities": ["sparse_vector"],
  "supported_parameters": ["dimensions", "encoding_format"],
  "parameters": {
      "max_tokens": 8192
  }
}

###

### 2.2 列出所有提供商模型
GET {{providerModelsEp}}?limit=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 2.3 查询单个提供商模型
GET {{providerModelsEp}}/{{fixedProviderModelId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 2.4 更新提供商模型
POST {{providerModelsEp}}/{{fixedProviderModelId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "capabilities": ["vision", "tools"],
    "is_active": true
}

###

### 2.5 删除提供商模型
DELETE {{providerModelsEp}}/{{fixedProviderModelId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###


### ============================================================
### 3. VirtualModel（虚拟模型）
### ============================================================

### 3.1 创建虚拟模型
# @name create_virtual_model
POST {{virtualModelsEp}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "global-chat",
    "description": "多后端加权负载均衡，主 DeepSeek 80% + 备 Gemini 20%",
    "model_type": "chat",
    "routing_strategy": "load_balance",
    "backends": [
        { "provider_model_id": "{{fixedProviderModelId}}", "weight": 80, "priority": 0 }
    ]
}

###

### 3.2 列出所有虚拟模型（含后端详情）
GET {{virtualModelsEp}}?limit=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 3.3 查询单个虚拟模型
GET {{virtualModelsEp}}/{{fixedVirtualModelId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 3.4 更新虚拟模型
POST {{virtualModelsEp}}/{{fixedVirtualModelId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "global-chat (Updated)"
}

###

### 3.5 删除虚拟模型
DELETE {{virtualModelsEp}}/{{fixedVirtualModelId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###


### ============================================================
### 4. RequestLog（请求日志 & 审计）
### ============================================================

### 4.1 查询请求日志
# 可用参数: ?status=completed&request_model=global-chat&limit=20&starting_after=abc...
GET {{requestLogsEp}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 4.2 查询日志详情（含完整 GatewayContext 审计快照）
GET {{requestLogsEp}}/{{fixedRequestLogId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 4.3 删除日志记录
DELETE {{requestLogsEp}}/{{fixedRequestLogId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###


### ============================================================
### 5. Apps & Keys（应用与鉴权密钥）
### ============================================================

# === 应用 (App) 操作 ===

### 5.1 创建应用
# @name create_app
POST {{appsEp}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Production App",
    "allowed_model_ids": ["{{fixedVirtualModelId}}"]
}

###

### 5.2 列出所有应用
GET {{appsEp}}?limit=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 5.3 查询单个应用
GET {{appsEp}}/{{fixedAppId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 5.4 更新应用
POST {{appsEp}}/{{fixedAppId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Production App (Updated)",
    "is_active": true
}

###

### 5.5 删除应用
DELETE {{appsEp}}/{{fixedAppId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

# === 密钥 (API Key) 操作 ===

### 5.6 创建 API Key
# @name create_api_key
POST {{appsEp}}/{{fixedAppId}}/keys HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "PROD Server Key",
    "expires_at": "2026-12-31T23:59:59Z"
}

###

### 5.7 列出某应用下的所有 API Key
GET {{appsEp}}/{{fixedAppId}}/keys?limit=10 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 5.8 获取某个具体 Key
GET {{appsEp}}/{{fixedAppId}}/keys/{{fixedApiKeyId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 5.9 更新 API Key
POST {{appsEp}}/{{fixedAppId}}/keys/{{fixedApiKeyId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "is_active": false
}

###

### 5.10 轮换 API Key（重新生成明文，旧的立即失效覆盖）
POST {{appsEp}}/{{fixedAppId}}/keys/{{fixedApiKeyId}}/rotate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 5.11 删除 API Key
DELETE {{appsEp}}/{{fixedAppId}}/keys/{{fixedApiKeyId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###


### ============================================================
### 6. Copilot OAuth（设备流授权扩展）
### ============================================================

### 6.1 生成设备验证码 (Device Code)
# @name create_device_code
POST {{oauthCopilotEp}}/device-codes HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 6.2 轮询设备验证状态 (Poll)
POST {{oauthCopilotEp}}/device-codes/{{deviceCode}}/poll HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "provider_id": "{{fixedProviderId}}"
}

###

### 6.3 验证凭据有效性 (Verify)
POST {{oauthCopilotEp}}/verify HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "provider_id": "{{fixedProviderId}}"
}

###


### ============================================================
### 7. Stats（统计分析）
### ============================================================

### 7.1 概览统计
GET {{statsEp}}/overview?range=1h HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 7.2 时序数据
GET {{statsEp}}/time-series?range=24h&interval=10m HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 7.3 错误分析
GET {{statsEp}}/errors?range=24h HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 7.4 Token 用量分析
GET {{statsEp}}/tokens?range=24h HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 7.5 今日实时统计（大数字卡片）
GET {{statsEp}}/today HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### 7.6 分组占比
GET {{statsEp}}/breakdown?range=24h&group_by=provider_model HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###
